title: Entire Floor 4BR/2BTH w/dishwasher near NW Ditmars!
posting_body: ['https://youtu.be/3aV0MLi0ALk', 'This is the video tour of the apartment.', ' Please note, apartments tend to look smaller on video than they actually are.', '*8 min walk from NW Ditmars Blvd', '*All hardwood floor except for kitchen and bathrooms', '*4 Bedrooms with 2 full bathroom!', '*One of the bedrooms have its own bathroom plus extra room for office, etc and fits king bed!', "*All other bedrooms can fit Queen, however no closet space so you'd need to bring your own dresser", '*Triple exposure, the only apartment on this 1st floor', '*Dishwasher and microwave in the kitchen', "*Near all of Astoria's hot spots, yet quiet treeelined street*Cats ok, no dogs", '*', 'No guarantors - you must have 40X ($144K/yr) or above total household income on your own with good credit', "Please email with your name, phone number (required - we won't contact you back without this), tell us a little bit about you and whoever you'll be living with and the best time to view or if you're out of town and cannot be present, request zoom or video tour.", 'BROKER FEE APPLIES!']
